      "comment": "CROYDON REIGN (2) has a strong winning strike-rate over this journey with two wins and a placing from four tries. Placed last time (19.84) at Murray Bridge Straight in a Grade 6, finishing third and beaten 2.5 lengths. Rates a leading player. COMPTON STELLA (8) finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive before that in her strong 23.16 win at Mt Gambier over 400m. Has the ability and can find winning form again. CATCH MY DESIGN (1) has hit the frame at 12 of 25 starts and has won two of last three, the latest scoring (19.72) over 342m at Angle Park. Goes well from this draw. Meets a moderate line up and should run well. TENACIOUS DESIGN (7) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
